    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no chips, scratches, or dents. Inside, the cabin is pristine, featuring leather that remains supple and electronics that function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history and every component operating at peak performance. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
